    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for a discerning buyer. The exterior is flawless, with the original paint retaining a deep, showroom-quality shine and no visible chips or scratches. Inside, the cabin is equally pristine; the leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, and all interior components look and function as if they just left the factory. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. This is a collector-grade example that must be seen in person to be fully appreciated.",
