    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who values both performance and aesthetic integrity. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical precision and a well-preserved interior. This offering represents a superior balance of value and sophistication, having passed our comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and long-term reliability. We invite serious inquiries to experience this exemplary machine firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
