      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my awesome car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! It looks great and drives even better\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential for precise power distribution. The chassis remains composed with recent subframe reinforcement and VANOS servicing already completed. While showing honest signs of use, the drivetrain remains tight with linear power delivery and sharp throttle response. A driver-focused machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
