    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains its deep luster, complemented by a set of well-preserved alloy wheels, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather seating remains supple and supportive, showing only light, characteristic softening on the driver's bolster. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension absorbs road imperfections with ease. Having been serviced regularly with full records available, this is a dependable, high-quality driver\u2019s car ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
